        <item>
            <title>Version 1.2</title>
            <pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 12:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>1.2</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.2</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h2>What's New in Version 1.2</h2>
                <h3>Major Features</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Implemented new Status System with visual slider interface</li>
                    <li>Added full-featured Markdown Editor with toolbar and keyboard shortcuts</li>
                    <li>Enhanced copy functionality with multiple format options</li>
                </ul>
                
                <h3>Markdown Editor</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Added visual toolbar for common markdown operations</li>
                    <li>Implemented keyboard shortcuts:
                        <ul>
                            <li>⌘B for Bold</li>
                            <li>⌘I for Italic</li>
                            <li>⌘. for Quote</li>
                            <li>⌘⌥1/2/3 for Headers</li>
                            <li>⌘K for Links</li>
                            <li>⌘L for Lists</li>
                            <li>⌘⇧L for Numbered Lists</li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li>Added real-time preview mode</li>
                </ul>

                <h3>Copy Enhancement</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Added multiple copy formats:
                        <ul>
                            <li>Markdown - preserves formatting</li>
                            <li>Plain Text - strips formatting</li>
                            <li>Title Only - just the title</li>
                            <li>Title & Summary - for quick sharing</li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li>Added visual feedback for copy operations</li>
                    <li>Integrated with system clipboard</li>
                </ul>

                <h3>Status System</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Implemented new visual status slider</li>
                    <li>Added smooth transitions between states</li>
                    <li>Improved status validation and error handling</li>
                    <li>Enhanced visual feedback for status changes</li>
                </ul>

                <h3>Bug Fixes & Improvements</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Fixed bundle system type handling</li>
                    <li>Improved database operations reliability</li>
                    <li>Enhanced error handling and user feedback</li>
                    <li>Various UI and performance improvements</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
